snippet.title: Danganronpa Dreamland | Prologue Intro (Eng Sub)
snippet.description:
🌐Download Link (Prologue) : https://zephi.itch.io/danganronpa-dreamland
Lots of new characters and lots of names I had to learn over past few weeks, oh boy get ready for a new ride everybody! we're entering into new territory here 😁
This fangan is pretty much new in social media so you may find it hard to search about the characters yet since no other translations have been made for it. But hopefully, things will change in the future!
💚Patreon for WIPs :https://www.patreon.com/Zephirum
🤎The Ko-fi channel! :https://ko-fi.com/zephirum 
💜Discord Server : https://discord.gg/vE9AMGAunS
